Echo Bay Mines Ltd said itdiscovered a gold deposit in the Cove area near its McCoy goldmine in Nevada.    Echo Bay said it encountered gold in 39 of 42 drill holesat Cove. It said seven holes averaged 0.185 ounce gold a shortton and 1.8 ounces of silver, with the seven intersectionsaveraging 118 feet in thickness beneath 25 feet of overburden.    The discovery is on the McCoy property, one mile northeastof the McCoy open pit, heap leach gold mine, which is expectedto produce about 85,000 ounces of gold this year, Echo Baysaid. Reuter&#3;